<h2 id="what-is-unbounce">📋 What Is Unbounce?</h2>

Unbounce is a dedicated landing page platform built for marketers and operators who need high-converting pages without developer dependencies. Unlike Squarespace or Shopify's native page builders, Unbounce exists for one purpose: turning traffic into conversions through obsessively optimized landing experiences.

For luxury retail operators, this means dedicated pages for product launches, VIP access lists, trunk show registrations, and limited-edition drops—all built with conversion science baked into the DNA. The platform offers drag-and-drop building, A/B testing, AI-powered traffic routing, and integrations with the CRM and email tools luxury operators already use.

Founded in 2009, Unbounce has processed over 1.5 billion conversions and now serves as the landing page backbone for brands ranging from independent jewelers to multi-location fashion retailers. Their 2025 introduction of Smart Copy AI and enhanced e-commerce integrations makes the 2026 version particularly relevant for luxury product launches where messaging precision matters.

